Description: Isolates and refines clean spectral signatures from 
    single stained controls. Deals with autofluorescence contamination in 
    controls effectively. Unmix fcs files with ordinary or weighted least squares,
    or with the hallmark AutoSpectral approach to deal with autofluorescence and
    fluorophore variability on a per-cell basis.
